Strings.pinAndPair_text:
1. On your computer, tablet, or mobile phone, go to www.dazn.com/tv 
2. Enter the following 6 digit code and click the "sign in" button. After your pin code is verified, you will be automatically logged in and you will be able to start using DAZN for docomo. %{pin} 

If you would like to refresh your pin code, please go back to the previous page and click "d account" one more time.
